<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q28_v4" title="Q28_v4" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>Para controlar la cantidad de agua que se entrega a un invernadero, se instala un sistema de riego automático que puede funcionar en modo lento o en modo rápido. En modo lento suministra 500 L/h y en modo rápido 2000 L/h.</p>
    <p>La rapidez <m:math><m:mi>r</m:mi></m:math>, medida en litros por hora (L/h), se modela con la expresión <m:math><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:mfrac></m:math>, donde <m:math><m:mi>V</m:mi></m:math> es el volumen total de agua, en litros, y <m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:math> es la cantidad de horas en que se suministra ese volumen.</p>
    <p>Si, para cierto cultivo, el sistema se programa en modo rápido para entregar 1500 L de agua, ¿cuánto tiempo durará ese riego? Responde en minutos.</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">75 minutos<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. 75 minutos equivalen a 1,25 horas. En modo rápido, en 1,25 horas se entregan 2000 × 1,25 = 2500 L, y 2500 L no es igual a 1500 L.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">45 minutos<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! En modo rápido, el tiempo es 1500 ÷ 2000 = 0,75 horas. Como 0,75 horas equivalen a 45 minutos, esa opción entrega exactamente 1500 L.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">80 minutos<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. 80 minutos equivalen a 80 ÷ 60 = 1,333... horas. En modo rápido, en ese tiempo se entregan 2000 × 1,333... = 2666,7 L aproximadamente, y 2666,7 L no es igual a 1500 L.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">180 minutos<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. 180 minutos equivalen a 3 horas. En modo rápido, en 3 horas se entregan 2000 × 3 = 6000 L, y 6000 L no es igual a 1500 L.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar los datos</strong></p>
            <p>El sistema está en modo rápido, por lo tanto la rapidez es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2000</m:mn></m:math> L/h</p>
            <p>El volumen que se quiere entregar es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1500</m:mn></m:math> L</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Usar la fórmula</strong></p>
            <p>La relación dada es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:mfrac></m:math></p>
            <p>Despejando <m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:math>:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mi>r</m:mi></m:mfrac></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Reemplazar los valores</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1500</m:mn><m:mn>2000</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> horas</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,75</m:mn></m:math> horas</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Convertir horas a minutos</strong></p>
            <p>Como 1 hora = 60 minutos, entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>0,75</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, el riego dura 45 minutos.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es <strong>45 minutos</strong>, es decir, la <strong>opción B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>